mlx-vlm - https://github.com/Blaizzy/mlx-vlm

gmlx primarily uses mlx-vlm as an installed dependency, patched at runtime
(see gmlx/upstream_seams.py), but two modules carry code copied or ported
from it, with modifications:

- gmlx/server_patches/apc.py: the batched-eval store_kv_blocks replacement
  is a verbatim copy of mlx_vlm.apc.APCManager.store_kv_blocks with the
  per-block mx.eval hoisted into chunked batches.
- gmlx/thinking_budget.py: ported from mlx-vlm's ThinkingBudgetCriteria
  stopping-criteria callback, reworked as an mlx-lm logits processor.

